&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A fantastic opportunity has arisen for a dynamic and forward-thinking Occupational Therapist to work within the integrated Trauma and Orthopaedic Therapy Team at on the Ipswich Site at ESNEFT. The successful candidate will have proven experience of Trauma and Orthopaedics and working in the ever-changing, fast-paced environment of and acute trust. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role will include working within our Regional Spinal Centre as a part of a large and expanding Trauma and Orthopaedic Therapy Team. Caseload includes; complex poly-trauma, spinal injuries and working with multi-agencies including out of area colleagues. The role includes helping to deliver our 7 day integrated service including initiating and delivering service development; alongside working within the wider integrated therapy across acute and community services. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We look forward to hearing from you.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rebecca Denwood - 01473 704380&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
